1. Best practice for NSTrace 

a. set ssl vserver "vServer_Name" -sessReuse DISABLED
b. set ssl vserver "vServer_Name" -dh DISABLED
c. unbind ssl vserver "vServer_Name" -eccCurveName "ECC_Curve_Name"
e. packet size 0

option. start nstrace -size 0 -mode SSLPLAIN

articles : https://support.citrix.com/article/CTX116557 | https://support.citrix.com/article/CTX120668
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

2. Vrac command

tail -f \var\log\ns.log
cat aaad.debug
nsconmsg –d current –g pol_hits
set authentication vserver <VserverName>-AuthenticationDomain alex.company.fr

